  "questionProse": [
    "出力には何が含まれますか？"
  ],
  "hintsProse": [],
  "explanationProse": [
    "The [`.setDate()`](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/setDate) method sets the day of the month, based on the given instance's current month.\n\nIf a value is provided outside of the number of days available, the date instance month value will be adjusted (e.g. A `setDate(32)` in January will calculate as February 1st.)\n\n<aside class=\"hint\">`setDate` sets the day of the month, typically in the range 1-31.</aside>"
  ]
